import Navbar from './components/navbar.js'
import Hero from './components/hero'
import Footer from './components/footer.js'

function Home() {
    return (
        <>
            <Navbar />
            <main>
                <Hero title='13My Best friends in React components' description='3Example website with React components'/>
            </main>
            <Footer/>
        </>
        )
}

export default Home
